# ShopBridge
# install nuget package

#Connect with SQL Server
Step 1. Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer

#Convert into Json format at response time
Step 2. Newtonsoft.Json

#For Sorting Purpose
Step 3. System.Linq.Dynamic.Core

#Make jwt token
Step 4. Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authentication.JwtBearer


# Run the Database Structure
Step 1. Run the Database Structure from given file.

# Import Postman package to run the file
Step 1. import the postman package file to check the API sequence By.

# Run ShopBridge Application
Step 1. Get token from Login API
Step 2. Put token in header section of Product Item Save API
Step 3. Put token in header section of Product item Get By Id API
Step 4. Put token in header section of Product Item Update API
Step 5. Put token in header section of Product Item Delete API


